# Per HANDOFF-META-PIPELINE-KICKOFF-2026-05-12.md §4.P5.C.5 deliverable.
# Owners are auto-requested for review on any PR that touches files
# matching the corresponding pattern. Even though every owner is
# currently @zstnbb, declaring them explicitly per lane / target makes
# the social contract visible and lets external contributors see who
# "owns" each surface — which is what HANDOFF §4.P5.C.5 acceptance
# point #3 calls for ("CODEOWNERS covers all D0/S0 targets").
#
# GitHub treats the LAST matching rule as authoritative — narrower
# patterns at the bottom override broader patterns at the top.

